snippet.title: NEONSOMNIA Early Access Trailer
snippet.description:
I made another Gameboy Color game you can play for free in your browser, or download for free to play on any real hardware/emulation you want.

https://maxthetics.itch.io/neonsomnia

Explore a surreal dream world and see strange things. Inspired by Yume Nikki and created for itch.io's Dream Diary Jam 7
